    public class SCUIDefaultWizardController
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISCUIWizardFlowController
    This call is default implementation of ISCUIWizardFlowController provided by the framework. This controller works with frameworks client side wizard controller. asmishra

      • processRequest

        public SCUIWizardControllerResponse processRequest(SCUIWizardMetaData wizardMetaData,
                                                   SCUIContext uiContext)
                                            throws java.lang.Exception
        Description copied from interface: ISCUIWizardFlowController
        This method should handle all wizard requests. This method should should determine the type of call (start, next, previous, finish or cancel), wizard definition id, next page. And based on the next page, this method should return a SCUIWizardControllerResponse with URI as the next page to which the request would either be forwarded to or included. wizardMetaData uiContext wizard controller response
